exercises.answer:
In system/fvSchemes:

```
ddtSchemes
{
    default Euler;
}
```

Or for specific field:

```
ddtSchemes
{
    default         backward;
    ddt(T)          Euler;
}
```

This applies first-order Euler implicit to all fields (or just T in second example).
